Phoebe Cates https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phoebe_Cates 0 Phoebe Belle Cates (born July 16, 1963) is a former American film actress, singer and model known primarily for her roles in several 1980s films, most notably Fast Times at Ridgemont High and Gremlins.
